{"tid":1571560,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（純感謝）多謝今日幫過三隻小羊既家長","createTime":"2019-09-15T12:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T13:08:02.000Z","uid":176994,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8521e0e96296dca92e349532cd3eab3211b0b7a5","tid":1571560,"uid":176994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:48:20.000Z","msg":"小妹同朋友一齊發夢<br />\n去到中環已經打算離開<br />\n我地打算走<br />\n但又發現今日d狗痴撚曬線玩困獸鬥<br />\n跑上山又有埋伏<br />\n前後都有埋伏<br />\n係我地忙惘梗點算既時候<br />\n見到幾個家長都準備走<br />\n所以我地決定偷偷痴埋去跟佢地走<br />\n點知佢地發現左我地<br />\n然後佢地好好心帶埋我地由金鐘跑到返灣仔<br />\n（（個時我地小羊3隻真係唔知點好<br />\n<br />\n跑到返老銅以為安全<br />\n換曬衫準備沿路去炮台山<br />\n點知手足又話前面有伏<br />\n然後我地小羊3隻又好驚慌咁跟住跑<br />\n好彩係老銅教會對出遇到義載叔叔<br />\n佢車走左我地3隻小羊同2位巴打<br />\n<br />\n比我地安全咁離開個到<br />\n係呢到特別多謝你地既幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"45b07cb8e6a28099ec928db3c2c0b6e5775995b3","tid":1571560,"uid":230169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:49:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"5ff3c6e7528b40f2cfc2ab05f38c4ff42736c054","tid":1571560,"uid":290883,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"安全就好，"},{"pid":"f645f33567aeab8104df6661cd66c285faca2aca","tid":1571560,"uid":111644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:50:03.000Z","msg":"你又知唔會車你去強姦"},{"pid":"7aa0218505b5a38daa1ed9d051b582974f5b7f46","tid":1571560,"uid":230169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T12:50:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=